### LXVIII. HOW ONE WHO HEARS WITH MORE THAN USUAL ACUTENESS.

<span id="img_12800"></span> ![](img/12800.jpg)

When they would symbolise *a man who hears with more than usual
acuteness*, they portray A SHE-GOAT, for she respires \[hears?\] through
both her nostrils and ears.

